lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich were left to rue a number of missed chances in their Champions League last 16 first leg against Juventus on Tuesday after the Germans squandered a two-goal lead to draw 2-2 despite dominating for much of the game.

headline.print_headline: Wasteful Bayern Rue Missed Opportunity to Kill Off Juve
headline.main: Wasteful Bayern Rue Missed Opportunity to Kill Off Juve
